Read and adhere to all rules defined in the `.cursor/rules/` directory, including:
- `.cursor/rules/global.yaml` - Workspace-wide rules
- `.cursor/rules/backend.yaml` - Rules scoped to `apps/backend/**`
- Any other rule files in this directory

These rules take precedence and must be followed for all code changes and operations in this project.
